  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support South Asian Immigrant Rights</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Immigrants and refugees--especially South Asians and those perceived as Muslims--are under attack.  For the past 26 years, we have been supporting crucial services to South Asian immigrants, from immigration and citizenship assistance,  literacy, workforce, seniors and social services.  We have been hosting Know Your Rights workshops and citizenship workshops, because there has been an increase in the need since January 2017.  Help us support and serve our South Asian immigrant community!</narrative>
  </description>
